$\phi^{-2}$ term  & 7.8  & 23.6\% & $\phi^{-2} \approx 0.382$ \\
$\phi^{-3}$ term  & 4.8  & 14.6\% & $\phi^{-3} \approx 0.236$ \\
$\phi^{-4}$ term  & 3.0  & 9.0\%  & $\phi^{-4} \approx 0.146$ \\
Residual (additive) & 4.8 & 14.6\% & Non-$\phi$ noise \\
\bottomrule
\end{tabular}
\end{table}

This matches the 618:382 ratio found in both Riemann zeta fractal analysis and ZANS contraction dynamics.

